{"questionId":"9069818","questionHtml":"<p>What is the pressure, in Pa, inside a 1.0 m<sup>3</sup> cylinder containing 10 kg of H<sub>2</sub> (g) at 25 ºC?</p>\n<p><em>R</em> = 8.31 J K<sup>–1</sup> mol<sup>–1</sup>; <em>pV</em> = <em>nRT</em></p>\n<p>A. <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{1 \\times {{10}^4} \\times 8.31 \\times 25}}{{1.0 \\times {{10}^3}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>8.31</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>25</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.0</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{5 \\times {{10}^2} \\times 8.31 \\times 298}}{{1.0}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>5</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>8.31</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>298</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.0</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{1 \\times 8.31 \\times 25}}{{1.0 \\times {{10}^3}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>8.31</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>25</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.0</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</m